abstract: When Hunters sing songs together about the unspoken dialogue underlying their relationship, the result can be electric, as it was Tuesday night at Cake Shop.

lead_paragraph: Sexual energy drives many good songs, and when a male and female duo write and sing songs together about the unspoken dialogue underlying their relationship, the result can be electric.
